China News Agency Yinchuan July 26th (Yang Di) "Nine songs of the Yellow River thousands of lis, the waves from the end of the world."
The Yellow River, which has stirred up the pride of countless literates, has given birth to the beautiful and rich Ningxia Plain, and now Ningxia, which has the beauty of "Shangjiang South", is adhering to the concept of "ecological priority and green development" and pursuing the poetic "Yellow River Dream".
The “Bibo Dream” of the River Clear Water Show
"The world's Yellow River Fu Ningxia", the Yellow River through Ningxia 397 kilometers, is the nurturing side of the "mother river."
However, with the rapid advancement of industrialization and urbanization, the imbalance between the development and utilization of rivers and lakes and the protection of management, the chaos of excessive sewage discharge, the construction of the lake, and the encroachment of the water are highlighted, resulting in the black smell of the water, the excessive water quality, the dirty environment, and the ecological degradation.
Now, Ningxia is promoting the restoration of water ecology, and strives to restore the Yellow River water shuixiu river.
Water should be cut from the source.
In Ningxia Yinchuan, the local "standard + pollution control + strict control" approach, the industrial park sewage all achieved centralized treatment, urban sewage treatment plants all achieved a first-class A standard discharge, the city built-up area of black and odorous water body basically eliminated, successfully declared the third batch of China's black and odorous water demonstration city.
In addition, Ningxia fully implemented the river and lake long system in 2017, and now has achieved full coverage of the responsibility system of the five-level river and lake system in the counties and counties, and the long-term patrol of the river and lake has become the norm.
The 64-year-old Gu Jincheng, who lives in a village on the Yellow River, witnessed the change of the Yellow River: “The water before it smelled, and after the rectification, the odor was gone.”
Gu Jincheng said that the ecological environment is good, his life is more comfortable, and now he often goes to the Yellow River with his family for a walk and feels the blue sky.
The "Wetland Dream" of the Shaguo Xiangxiang
Birds, green trees, stacks, turquoise water... The beauty of Fan Zhongyan's "sand gulls in the Xiangjie" has become a reality in the Yellow River Wetland Park in Yinchuan, Ningxia.
The Yellow River through Ningxia, along the way to the formation of rivers and wetlands, lakes and wetlands, swamp wetlands and other wetlands, to promote the rational use of water resources and water ecological balance plays an important role, but also become an important international bird migration channel.
Since 2009, the relevant departments of Ningxia have invested a total of about 3.45 billion yuan in wetland protection projects, at present, Yinchuan wetland area of 19,200 hectares, wetland protection rate of 78.5%, there are natural lakes, swamp wetlands nearly 200, with 5 national wetland parks, 1 national urban wetland park, 6 autonomous region-level wetland parks, 8 municipal parks.
Lv Jinhu, deputy director of Yinchuan Wetland Protection Center, told reporters that wetland protection has increased biodiversity and is particularly evident in birds, "the gull is an endangered bird, only more than 20,000 in the world, of which Yinchuan Wetland is inhabited by more than 2,000."
At the same time, Ningxia has delineated a red line of 500 meters in the wetland protection area on both sides of the Yinchuan section of the Yellow River in accordance with the law, and stipulates that no unit or individual may carry out development, construction and business activities within the scope of protection except for public welfare projects.
Zhao Shaoyong, deputy director of Yinchuan Water Conservancy Service Center, introduced that through the pollution source management, comprehensive remediation of river and lake ecology and the construction of the end wetlands, the water quality of Ningxia's 9 main yellow drainage ditches has reached 100% of the Class IV standard, "now the water is also clear, the fish also swim, and the flowers are also opened."
The "Drinking Water Dream" of Inclusive People's Livelihoods
Ningxia Yinchuan City once had the title of "embarrassing": the only city along the Yellow City that "guarded the lack of water and drank the Yellow River".
Since 2010, Yinchuan City has been facing the continuous peak of summer water shortage problems, nearly a decade of "water shortage pain" has become a summer suffering experience for many high-floor residents, but in the major water sources in the limit of over-harvesting, urban underground has formed a large area of groundwater over-the-funnel area, water-based water shortage has become a problem that plagues Yinchuan City.
Thanks to the improvement of the water quality of the Yellow River, the water of the Yellow River after drinking and purification has become a good way to solve the problem of drinking water for local residents.
Ding Ming, deputy director of Yinchuan Municipal Water Bureau, introduced that in order to improve the demand for water for urban and rural residents of Yinchuan, Ningxia timely launched the water supply project of the urban and rural western line of Yinchuan Metropolitan Area, replacing the original groundwater source with high-quality Yellow River water.
"On December 29, 2019, the water supply project officially connected to the three districts of Yinchuan City, and in 2020, the residents of Minning Town and Helan County also drank the water of the Yellow River."
Ding Ming said that the Yinchuan water conservancy department will consider the transformation of regional rural drinking water and urban water supply integration, "the next step, we will integrate the scattered rural water supply points into the western water supply project, is expected to basically realize the Yinchuan area of urban and rural integrated water supply by the end of this year."
